<L>__{exterior fifth avenue apartment day}
<A>__{bud, in a suit, waits next to a motorcycle across from one of the most desirable addresses in new york. the doorman rushes to open the door under the canopy as a tall strong man in his fifties emerges with a lawyer type and a female executive. the man is sir lawrence wildman and his manner and gait convey the impression of an authoritative presence with little patience as the chauffeur opens the door and he slides into the back seat of the limo. buddy, astride marv's kawasaki 500, hits the streets after him. the music through the following montage should suggest a chase brio.}
